       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. FUNCTION-TRIM.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-STR    PIC X(15) VALUE "  Hello  ".
       01 WS-RESULT PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           MOVE FUNCTION TRIM(WS-STR) TO WS-RESULT
           DISPLAY "Trimmed: [" WS-RESULT "]"
           STOP RUN.
